## Important: Branch Mode

**NEVER push directly to the main/default branch.** You are working on a dedicated feature branch (already checked out). After committing and pushing your changes, use the `create_pull_request` tool to open a pull request. Do NOT use `gh pr create` or any other shell command.

If this task is related to an issue, reference it in the PR body (e.g., "Fixes #123").

Do NOT merge the PR yourself — let the reviewer handle that.
